{"id":568792,"date":[{"year":1978,"month":6,"day":1}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"201","ytitle":"","mtitle":"做新时期的好儿童","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1978\\06\\7861020601.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>小星星　亮晶晶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晶亮星星是卫星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卫星高高天上飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我驾卫星望北京。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1978\\06\\7861020602.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>攀登理论山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小不畏难；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习又实践，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦战能过关。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1978\\06\\7861020603.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>管天小组志气高，为农服务逞英豪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日日夜夜不辞苦，赢得赞誉切莫骄。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1978\\06\\7861020604.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>少先队旗红艳艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗一角飘胸前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学好文化爱科学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长大实现先烈愿。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1978\\06\\7861020605.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>小火箭，尖又尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕云播雨赛神仙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日我做小火箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来日宇航上九天。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1978\\06\\7861020606.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>少年号　气垫船，斩风劈浪无阻拦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河川湖海任我过，沙漠绿洲任往还。(本报记者摄影、配诗)</FONT>"}]}